/span><span style="color: #00a022">Cæturcēlienu</span> </span><span class="moze-tiny" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">(kas)</span></b></p><p><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Čóms</span><span class="moze-tiny" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> (čoms) </span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">---&gt; </span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #00a022">Savinieks</span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">, </span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #00a022">sebris</span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> [<a href="https://tezaurs.lv/sebris:2" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">1</a>][<a href="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/914626264336334888/1116471154840969286/PXL_20230608_160107542.MP2.jpg?ex=69c1008a&amp;is=69bfaf0a&amp;hm=aca340b04931ac31ead74564caf21fd86b5f8d440cdc143654125942caf0da1a&amp;" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">2</a>][<a href="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/914626264336334888/1116475318388134050/PXL_20230608_2112320742.jpg?ex=69c1046b&amp;is=69bfb2eb&amp;hm=7f79048de681d68ec7ad0eea787b2a211b66c09b40a0d46cf904759b60c80ea3&amp;" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">3</a>][<a href="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/914626264336334888/1116475353632886804/PXL_20230608_211247953.MP2.jpg?ex=69c10473&amp;is=69bfb2f3&amp;hm=1ec20b0faff04ef4acce4ddc098c0c352325d8e512a2b994847c29f705e0b57c&amp;" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">4</a>][5 (savs, svešs)], savris</span></p>
        <h1 style="text-align: left;"><b><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #000000">D</span></span></b></h1><p><b><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #000000">Dabūt ---&gt; (</span><span style="color: #00a022">Ie</span><span style="color: #000000">)</span><span style="color: #00a022">gūt</span><span style="color: #000000"> </span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-tiny">(vārtus, kurpes, vietu, redzēt, dzirdēt)</span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #000000">, </span><span style="color: #00a022">tikt pie</span><span style="color: #000000"> </span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-tiny">(lielas naudas) </span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large">| (</span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">Ie</span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large">)</span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">gūt</span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large">, </span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">saņemt</span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-tiny"> (pa sāniem/purnu)</span></b></p>
          <p><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000">Datōrs </span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-tiny">(dators)</span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"> ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Skaitļoklis</span><span style="color: #000000"> </span></span><span class="moze-tiny"><span style="color: #000000"><b>(jau æsošais vārds „</b><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/skait%C4%BCot%C4%81js" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" style="font-weight: bold;">skaitļotājs</a><b>”, bet ar rīka, nevis darītāja (dzīva) izskaņu)</b></span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"><br>Lieldatōrs ---&gt; Lielskaitļoklis<b><span style="text-align: start; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal">, </span></b>skaitļotne, skaitļotava</span></span></p>
