gn: left; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal"> </span></span><span style="text-align: left; font-style: normal;" class="moze-tiny"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">(elektrošoka pistole)<b> ---&gt; </b></span></span><span style="font-weight: bold; text-align: left; font-style: normal;"><span style="color: #00a022" class="moze-large">Strāvekļšautuks </span><span class="moze-tiny"><span style="color: #000000">(sk. aizvietojumu vārdam „pistole”)</span></span></span><span style="font-weight: bold; text-align: left; font-style: normal;" class="moze-tiny"><span style="color: #000000">, </span></span><span style="font-weight: bold; text-align: left; font-style: normal;"><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large">[sarunvalodai]</span></span><span style="font-weight: bold; text-align: left; font-style: normal;" class="moze-tiny"><span style="color: #000000"> </span></span><span style="font-weight: bold; text-align: left; font-style: normal;"><span style="color: #00a022" class="moze-large">strāveklene</span></span><br></span></p>
