, 0);" class="moze-tiny">(zviedzos nost, jeb 'zviedzos līdz nāvei, lejup arba nost no kaut kā')</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">, </span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">Rcn</span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large"> </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-tiny">(rǣcos nost)</span><br><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">Rófl </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-tiny">(rofl, rolling on the floor laughing)</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large"> ---&gt; </span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">Zvr</span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large"> </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-tiny">(zviegdams ripinos)</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">, </span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">rrc</span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large"> </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-tiny">(rǣkdams ripinos)</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">, zvd </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-tiny">(zviedzu dirsā)</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">, Dzv&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-tiny">(dirsā zviedzu)</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">, drc<span class="moze-large"> </span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-tiny">(dirsā rǣcu)</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">, zvp </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-tiny">(zviedzos prom, projām)</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">, rcp </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-tiny">(rǣcu prom/projām)</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">, azv </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-tiny">(aizzviedzos)</span><span style="