”)[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/m%C4%81ma" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">APVV-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">] {„Māmu, atnāksi lūdzu?”}</span></span></b></p><p><b><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #000000">Manta ---&gt; [Tas, kas kādam pied</span><span class="moze-tiny" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span class="moze-large"><span class="moze-large">ær; īpašums]&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: #00a022">Turta</span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large"> </span><span style="color: #000000"><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/turta" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" style=""><span class="moze-tiny">[APVV-T]</span></a><span class="moze-tiny"> [</span><a href="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/914626264336334888/1285995117634912306/PXL_20240916_220336228.MP.jpg?ex=69be1908&amp;is=69bcc788&amp;hm=56c81885a86984ee27875b8f6d165c275677f3d3378ee1c04f1b5da7ef076383&amp;" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" style=""><span class="moze-tiny">IZC-K</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">]&nbsp;</span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large">/ [Aizderīgu lietu kopums arba liels daudzums, kas kādam pieder, jeb bagātība] </span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">Turtība</span><span style="color: #000000"> / </span></span><span class="moze-large" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">[priekšm</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span class="moze-large">æ</span></span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #000000">ts, lieta] </span><span style="color: #00a022">lieta</span><span style="color: #000000">, [sarunvalodai] </span><span style="color: #00a022">daikts</span><br><span style="color: #000000">Mantīgs ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Turtīgs</span><br><span style="color: #000000">Mantība ---&gt;</span><span style="color: #00a022"> Turtība</span><br></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large">Mantnīca ---&gt; </span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a02