000"> | [ilgstoši, vairākās vietās] </span><span style="color: #00a022">Graustīt<br></span>Postīgs, postošs ---&gt; <span style="color: #00a022">Ārdošs</span>, <span style="color: #00a022">nīcinošs</span><br><span style="color: #000000">Nopostīt ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Noārdīt</span><span style="color: #000000">, </span><span style="color: #00a022">nonīcināt</span><span style="color: #000000"> </span></span><span style="color: #000000"><span class="moze-tiny">(</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/non%C4%ABcin%C4%81t" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">apvv.</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">)</span></span><span class="moze-large"><br><span style="color: #000000">Sapostīt --&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Sagraut</span><span style="color: #000000">, </span><span style="color: #00a022">saārdīt</span><span style="color: #000000">, </span><span style="color: #00a022">sanīcināt</span><span style="color: #000000"> </span></span><span style="color: #000000"><span class="moze-tiny">(</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/san%C4%ABcin%C4%81t" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">apvv.</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">)</span></span><span class="moze-large"><br><span style="color: #000000">Izpostīt ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Izārdīt</span><span style="color: #000000">, </span><span style="color: #00a022">iznīcināt</span><br><span style="color: #000000">Postījums ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Ārdījums</span><span style="color: #000000">, </span><span style="color: #00a022">nīcinājums<br></span>Postītājs ---&gt; <span style="color: #00a022">Ārdītājs</span>, <span style="color: #00a022">nīcinātājs</span><br><span style="color: #000000">Posts ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Zudība</span><span style="color: #000000">, </span><span style="color: #00a022">nīcība</span><span style="color: #000000"> / </span><span style="color: #00a022">Nelaime</span><br><span style="color: #000000